sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant E as Express API
    participant S as AuthService
    participant D as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    C->>E: POST /auth/login (email, password)
    E->>S: login(email, password)
    S->>D: findUnique({ where: { email } })
    D-->>S: User Data + Password Hash
    S->>S: bcrypt.compare()
    S-->>E: JWT Token + User Data
    E-->>C: Response 200 { success: true, token: "..." }
    Note over C: User authenticatedsequenceDiagram
